    "This underscores the critical role of continued research in this domain.",
    "Finally, the affordability, usability and ease-of-use of such systems are critical considerations.",
    "While our ap-plication currently utilizes models offered by OpenAI, LEAP will soon be adapted to incorporate LLMs from other providers, particularly free LLMs, thereby increasing accessibility.",
